dct_title_s: Guía Peuser plano capital federal y alrededores
dct_description_sm: Oriented with north towards lower right5000 Map shows administrative [partidos] boundaries, street names, subways stations, and railroads. Includes location map. Map of Buenos Aires on verso shows three classes of roads, and train stop stations.
